		"underground": {
			// VSDune: kill soil in underground ruin schematics.
			// Vanilla underground ruins ship plant-bed dirt and grass-
			// covered soil (kitchens, gardens, mass graves with topsoil
			// caps, etc.). On Arrakis those read as anachronistic patches
			// of fertile ground inside the dunes. Remap every soil
			// variant (5 fertility x 4 grasscoverage = 20 codes) to the
			// local sand-rocktype so the rooms read as buried in sand
			// instead of containing dirt. Same `{rock}` substitution
			// pattern the existing ore remaps use - the cave-attached
			// placement resolves {rock} to the surrounding rock type
			// and emits sand-{rock}, which the worldgen already paints
			// elsewhere via blocklayers (so the textures match).
			"soil-verylow-none":         "sand-{rock}",
